ActPublic Safety Act, 2002
SubjectBill C-7 - Part 8 (Export and Import Permits Act) ** COMING INTO FORCE **
PrecisOrder fixing MARCH 31, 2007 as the day on which Part 8 of the Public Safety Act, 2002, being chapter 15 of the Statutes of Canada, 2004 [BILL C-7], which makes amendments to the Export and Import Permits Act, COMES INTO FORCE. . BILL C-7 -- ROYAL ASSENT: MAY 6, 2004
